Class VoteController

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • VoteController

  • public class VoteController
extends javafx.application.Application
    This Vote Controller is the controller class for the Vote interface. After the user has chosen the state and the precinct on the previous interface, the ballot will appear. The positions and candidates for those positions will be listed based on the selected state and precinct. After the candidates are selected and the vote button is pressed, the program will register the vote to the database and the program will return to the main menu. This class inherits the Application class.
    Author:
    Sophia Mallaro
